name: Jenkins - Job Information
description: The Jenkins - Job Information dashboard provides detailed information into specific jobs. Panels display information on job URLs, duration trends, execution results, test case trends, slowest stages for pipeline jobs, console logs, and common errors.

panels.name: Total Success
Test Cases
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "number", "result" as Name, Number, Result
| where name = {{Name}}
| json "testResult.failures", "testResult.passes", "testResult.skips", "testResult.total" as Failed, Passed, Skipped, Total
| avg(Failed) as Failed, avg(Passed) as Passed, avg(Skipped) as Skipped, avg(Total) as Total by Number
| toLong(Number)
| sort by Number asc
| concat("#", Number) as Number

panels.name: Top 10 Failed Stages with Common Errors
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Pipeline_Stages {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where name = {{Name}}
| json "stages" as StagesPipeline
| parse regex field = StagesPipeline "(?<json_added_blob>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi
| json field=json_added_blob "id", "name", "startTime", "duration", "status", "steps", "error" as %"Stage ID", %"Stage Name", %"Start Time", %"Stage Duration", %"Stage Status", %"Stage Steps", %"Stage Error" nodrop
| where !(%"Stage Status" matches "SUCCESS")
| replace (%"Stage Error", ",", "\n") as %"Stage Error"
| count as Count by %"Stage Name", %"Stage Error"
| limit 10

panels.name: Total Builds
Recent Commits
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Scm_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "jobName" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}}
| json "eventTime", "changeLog" as Time, Commit
| where Commit != "[]"
| replace(Commit, ",", "\n\n") as Commit
| replace(Commit, "author", "\nauthor") as Commit
| replace(Commit, "message", "\nmessage") as Commit
| replace(Commit, "[", "") as Commit
| replace(Commit, "]", "") as Commit
| count by Master, Time, Commit
| sort by Time
| fields - _count
| limit 10

panels.name: Top 5 Slowest Stages by Average Run Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Pipeline_Stages {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}}
| json "stages" as StagesPipeline
| parse regex field = StagesPipeline "(?<json_added_blob>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi
| json field=json_added_blob "id", "name", "startTime", "duration", "status", "steps" as %"Stage ID", %"Stage Name", %"Start Time", %"Stage Duration", %"Stage Status", %"Stage Steps" nodrop
| avg(%"Stage Duration") as %"Stage Duration in seconds" by %"Stage Name"
| sort by %"Stage Duration in seconds"
| limit 5

panels.name: Total Failures
Result by Execution Node
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}}
| json "nodeName", "result" as %"Node Name", Result
| if(Result matches "SUCCESS", 1, 0) as Success
| if(Result matches "FAILURE", 1, 0) as Failure
| if(Result matches "ABORTED", 1, 0) as Aborted
| if(Result matches "UNSTABLE", 1, 0) as Unstable
| count as Total_Logs, sum(Success) as Successes, sum(Failure) as Failures, sum(Aborted) as Abort, sum(Unstable) as Unstable by %"Node Name"
| (Successes/Total_Logs) as Successful
| (Failures/Total_Logs) as Failed
| (Abort/Total_Logs) as Aborted
| (Unstable/Total_Logs) as Unstable
| fields %"Node Name", Successful, Failed, Aborted, Unstable

panels.name: Top 5 Failed Tests
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Test_Result {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}}
| json "testResult" as statusValues
| parse regex field=statusValues "(?<TestResult>\{[^\}]+\})" multi
| json auto field=TestResult
| className as %"Class Name" | testName as %"Test Name"| duration/60 as %"Test Duration" | status as %"Test Status"
| where %"Test Status" matches "Failed"
| concat(%"Class Name", ".", %"Test Name") as %"Test Name"
| count as Count by %"Test Name"
| sort by Count
| limit 5

panels.name: Recent Configuration Changes
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Config_Change {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "userId", "userName", "eventTime", "message", "fileDetails.Old_File_Data", "fileDetails.Current_File_Data" as %"User Id", %"User Name", Time, %"Config Message", %"Old File Data", %"Current File Data" nodrop
| parse field=%"Config Message" "* changed configuration for the file jobs/*/config.xml." as User, Name
| where Name matches {{Name}}
| base64Decode(%"Old File Data") as %"Old File Data"
| base64Decode(%"Current File Data") as %"Current File Data"
| count by Time, Master, %"User Id", %"User Name", %"Current File Data", %"Old File Data"
| sort by Time
| fields - _count
| limit 10

panels.name: Average Run Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "jobRunDuration", "result" as Name, Duration, Result
| where Name = {{Name}}
| Duration/60 as Duration
| timeslice 10m
| avg(Duration) as %"Duration in minutes" by _timeslice
| fillmissing timeslice(10m)
| outlier %"Duration in minutes"

panels.name: Recent Console Logs
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc
| _sourceHost as Master
| _sourceName as SourceName
| where SourceName matches "{{Name}}#*" 
| parse field=_raw "[*] *" as Time, %"Log Message"
| trim (%"Log Message")
| count by Time, Master, %"Log Message"
| sort by Time
| fields Time, Master, %"Log Message"
| limit 50

panels.name: Job Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name", "number", "result", "jobRunDuration" as Name, Number, Result, Duration
| where name = {{Name}}
| Duration/60 as Duration
| avg(Duration) as %"Duration in minutes" by Number
| toLong(Number)
| sort by Number asc
| concat("#", Number) as Number

panels.name: Top 5 Slowest Test by Average Run Duration
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Test_Result {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}}
| json "testResult" as statusValues
| parse regex field=statusValues "(?<TestResult>\{[^\}]+\})" multi
| json auto field=TestResult
| className as %"Class Name" | testName as %"Test Name"| duration/60 as %"Test Duration" | status as %"Test Status"
| concat(%"Class Name", ".", %"Test Name") as %"Test Name"
| avg(%"Test Duration") as %"Test Duration in minutes" by %"Test Name"
| sort by %"Test Duration in minutes"
| limit 5

panels.name: Job URL
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}} 
| first(_raw) as message by Name, Master
| parse regex field=message "\"(?<Key>.*?)\":(?<Value>.*?),"  multi
| where key in ("jobBuildURL", "upstreamJobURL", "hudsonVersion")
| json field=message "jobBuildURL", "number" as URL, number
| replace(URL, concat("/",number,"/"), "") as URL
| concat(URL, "/configure") as Config_URL
| if(key="hudsonVersion" , Config_URL, Value) as Value
| replace(Value, "\"", "") as Value
| parse field=URL "*://*/" as domain, url_base nodrop
| if(key="upstreamJobURL" , if(isEmpty(value), "",concat(domain, "://",url_base,"/",Value)), Value) as Value
| if(Key="hudsonVersion", "CONFIG URL", if(Key="jobBuildURL", "BUILD URL", "UPSTREAM JOB URL")) as Key
| if(isEmpty(value) ,"-", tourl(Value, Key)) as URL
| where URL != "-"
| fields Master, URL

panels.name: Job Status Percentage
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "name" as Name
| where Name = {{Name}}
| json "result" as Result
| if(Result matches "SUCCESS", 1, 0) as Success
| if(Result matches "FAILURE", 1, 0) as Failure
| if(Result matches "ABORTED", 1, 0) as Aborted
| if(Result matches "UNSTABLE", 1, 0) as Unstable
| timeslice 10m
| count as Total_Logs, sum(Success) as Successes, sum(Failure) as Failures, sum(Aborted) as Abort, sum(Unstable) as Unstable by _timeslice
| (Successes/Total_Logs) as Successful
| (Failures/Total_Logs) as Failed
| (Abort/Total_Logs) as Aborted
| (Unstable/Total_Logs) as Unstable
| fields _timeslice, Successful, Failed, Aborted, Unstable

panels.name: Common Log Errors
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc
| _sourceHost as Master
| _sourceName as SourceName
| where SourceName matches "{{Name}}#*"
| parse field=_raw "[*] *" as Time, %"Log Message"
| trim (%"Log Message")
| where %"Log Message" matches "*WARNING*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*ERROR*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*fail*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*warning*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*error*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*fail*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*Exception*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*Fail*" OR %"Log Message" matches "*Error*"
| count as Count by Master, %"Log Message"
| sort by Count
| limit 10

panels.name: Max Run Duration
Recent Builds
panels.queryString:
$$jenkinslogsrc Job_Status {{Name}}
| _sourceHost as Master
| json "jobRunDuration", "number", "result", "name", "jobBuildURL" as %"Duration in minutes", Number, Result, Name, URL
| where Name = {{Name}}
| tourl(URL, Name) as Name
| if(Result matches "SUCCESS", ":white-heavy-check-mark:", ":prohibited:") as icon
| lookup utf as Result from https://s3.amazonaws.com/sumologic-app-data/emoji.csv on shortname=icon
| count by Master, Name, Number, Result, _messageTime
| sort by _messageTime
| fields - _count, _messageTime
